<h2><a name="struct" id="struct">struct</a></h2>
<div class="level2">

<p>
Sintassi:
</p>
<pre class="c code c++" style="font-family:monospace;">    <span class="kw4">struct</span> struct<span class="sy0">-</span>name <span class="sy0">:</span> inheritance<span class="sy0">-</span>list <span class="br0">&#123;</span>
      public<span class="sy0">-</span>members<span class="sy0">-</span>list<span class="sy0">;</span>
    protected<span class="sy0">:</span>
      protected<span class="sy0">-</span>members<span class="sy0">-</span>list<span class="sy0">;</span>
    private<span class="sy0">:</span>
      private<span class="sy0">-</span>members<span class="sy0">-</span>list<span class="sy0">;</span>
    <span class="br0">&#125;</span> object<span class="sy0">-</span>list<span class="sy0">;</span></pre>
<p>
Le strutture definite con <code>struct</code> sono come classi, tranne che per il fatto che i membri di una <code>struct</code>
sono per default pubblici invece che privati. In C le <code>struct</code> possono solo contenere dati e non possono avere liste
di eredit√†.
</p>

<p>
Le strutture possono essere definite senza dover esplicitamente creare istanze di nuovi oggetti. Nell&#039;esempio che segue il codice crea un nuovo tipo di dati chiamato <strong>Date</strong> e crea un istanza di <strong>Date</strong> chiamata <strong>today</strong>:
</p>
<pre class="c code c++" style="font-family:monospace;">     <span class="kw4">struct</span> Date <span class="br0">&#123;</span>
       <span class="kw4">int</span> day<span class="sy0">;</span>
       <span class="kw4">int</span> month<span class="sy0">;</span>
       <span class="kw4">int</span> year<span class="sy0">;</span>
     <span class="br0">&#125;</span> today<span class="sy0">;</span>
&nbsp;
     <span class="kw4">int</span> main<span class="br0">&#40;</span><span class="br0">&#41;</span> <span class="br0">&#123;</span>
        today.<span class="me1">day</span> <span class="sy0">=</span> <span class="nu0">4</span><span class="sy0">;</span>
        today.<span class="me1">month</span> <span class="sy0">=</span> <span class="nu0">7</span><span class="sy0">;</span>
        today.<span class="me1">year</span> <span class="sy0">=</span> <span class="nu0">1776</span><span class="sy0">;</span>
     <span class="br0">&#125;</span></pre>
<p>
